52
00:04:33,107 --> 00:04:37,152
Okay. So,
how long has it been there?

53
00:04:40,215 --> 00:04:44,022
Blood stopped pooling, still wet...
couple hours at the most.

54
00:04:44,065 --> 00:04:45,663
What time was it found?

55
00:04:45,706 --> 00:04:48,520
A jogger called it in
this morning about 7:30.

56
00:04:48,665 --> 00:04:52,292
No prints. Wiped clean.
Real creep show, huh?

57
00:04:52,336 --> 00:04:54,071
Any sign of the
rest of the body?

58
00:04:54,218 --> 00:04:58,072
Just Mr. Hand.
Do you think this is our guy's work?

59
00:04:58,215 --> 00:04:59,832
The ice-truck killer?

60
00:05:00,575 --> 00:05:03,682
It's hard to say. There's blood.
That's different.

61
00:05:04,188 --> 00:05:07,573
Plus, it's a male victim --
haven't seen that before.

62
00:05:07,677 --> 00:05:10,912
