She loved it.

739
00:54:44,445 --> 00:54:45,792
You nailed that one.

740
00:55:11,586 --> 00:55:15,352
<i>Everyone hides who they are,
at least some of the time.

741
00:55:19,377 --> 00:55:22,200
<i>Sometimes you bury that
part of yourself so deeply

742
00:55:22,387 --> 00:55:25,820
<i>that you have to be
reminded it's there at all.

743
00:55:35,928 --> 00:55:39,220
