750
00:56:17,088 --> 00:56:19,202
<i>but I did.

751
00:56:27,617 --> 00:56:31,412
<i>I'm not the monster
he wants me to be.

752
00:56:31,545 --> 00:56:34,463
<i>So I'm neither man nor beast.

753
00:56:35,255 --> 00:56:38,021
<i>I'm something new entirely,

